The evidence with the title 'McCain votes with Bush? - FactCheck.org ' says Jun 13, 2008  ... Barack Obama ( june 3): It's not change when John McCain decided to stand with George Bush 95 percent of the time, as he did in the Senate last year. The claim is true. According to Congressional Quarterly's Voting Studies, in 2007 McCain voted in line with the president's position 95 percent of the time  ... 
